"Get-Service"
    - Lists every Windows service and whether it's running or stopped.

"Restart-Service Spooler"
    - Restarts the Print Spooler (common printer fix).

"Start-Service"
    - Starts a stopped Windows service.

"Stop-Service"
    - Stops a running Windows service.

"Get-Service | Where {$_.Status -eq "Stopped"}"
    - Finds every stopped service on the machine.
